ld wreck</span> even greater <span style="font-size: 14.6667px;">calamity on the human race</span> than could persistent radiation. AIDS and ebola viruses are just a small example of recently emerging plagues with no known cure or vaccine. Can we imagine hundreds of such plagues? <span style="font-size: 14.6667px;">HUMAN EXTINCTION IS NOW POSSIBLE</span>.</span>

